											<div class="contenttext"><p>Thank you for your feedback, Barbara.</p>
<p>&gt; I&rsquo;ve noticed no image appears in the emails to subscribers. Is that intentional? Is there a setting to turn it back on?</p>
<p>Could you please share the details with us? For instance, would it be possible to send us a screenshot of an email that is missing the image and the device / email client name (e.g. Outlook / Mail app on macOS, &hellip;)? You can use the <a href="mailto:help@wordpress.com">help@wordpress.com</a> email address and we will happy to take a closer look.</p>
<p>Generally, Featured images are not displayed in the &ldquo;New Post&rdquo; notification email.</p>
<p>Cheers.</p>
